Available Tools: open_garage | close_garage | get_garage_status | set_garage_timer
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "door_id": "string", "delay_seconds": number }
Response Schema: { "door_id": "string", "state": "open|closed|opening|closing", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Can you tell me if the north entry garage is open right now?
Call: { "func_call": "get_garage_status", "door_id": "garage_north_05", "delay_seconds": 0 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_north_05", "state": "closed", "timestamp": "2023-11-01T09:15:30Z" }

Question: Program the east wing door to shut automatically in 8 minutes.
Call: { "func_call": "set_garage_timer", "door_id": "garage_east_06", "delay_seconds": 480 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_east_06", "state": "open", "timestamp": "2023-11-01T09:18:45Z" }

Question: What is the current status of the storage unit garage door?
Call: { "func_call": "get_garage_status", "door_id": "garage_storage_07", "delay_seconds": 0 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_storage_07", "state": "closing", "timestamp": "2023-11-01T09:22:10Z" }

Question: I need the north entry door to close in 3 minutes please.
Call: { "func_call": "set_garage_timer", "door_id": "garage_north_05", "delay_seconds": 180 }
